txt.en: Defeat many wights in Imlad Morgul.

'It is said the wights of sacrificial victims walk the paths among Bâr Nírnaeth, the Houses of Lamentation, searching in vain for a peace that will never be theirs. But that is, of course, ridiculous.' - Gandalf
